@startuml
title Sequence 09 - Mengisi Jurnal Aktivitas Harian Placement Aktif
autonumber
actor Mahasiswa
participant "Frontend Portal\nLaporan" as FE
participant "Placement API\n/api/v1/placements" as API
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "Storage\nlocal/S3" as Storage

Mahasiswa -> FE: Buka halaman Jurnal/Laporan
FE -> API: GET /placements/me
API -> DB: Query placements by student_id
DB --> API: Daftar placement
FE -> API: GET /placements/{placement_id}/logs
API -> DB: Query ActivityLogs by placement_id
DB --> API: Jurnal harian
API --> FE: Logs
FE --> Mahasiswa: Tampilkan jurnal

Mahasiswa -> FE: Tambah jurnal dan lampiran
FE -> API: POST /placements/{placement_id}/logs
API -> DB: Validasi placement milik mahasiswa
API -> DB: Insert ActivityLogs(description_raw, duration_minutes)
DB --> API: log_id
opt upload lampiran
  FE -> API: POST /placements/{placement_id}/logs/{log_id}/attachment
  API -> Storage: Simpan file lampiran
  Storage --> API: attachment_url
  API -> DB: Update ActivityLogs.attachment_url
end
API --> FE: Jurnal tersimpan
FE --> Mahasiswa: Tampilkan sukses
@enduml
